addToRestrictWords(string[]).details: Adds words (without .jfin) to the list of restricted words.

constructor.details: Initializes contract with addresses of admin and data storage contracts. Also pre-populates the whitelist with characters and numbers.

hashedTakedownList().details: Retrieves the list of all takedown hashes from the data store.
